entry.title: Nuclear Plant at Risk as Ukraine and Russia Gear Up for Spring Offensive
entry.content: Military activity is increasing around the Zaporizhzhia nuclear-power plant, according to international atomic energy officials, as Ukrainian and Russian forces gear up for an expected increase in fighting this spring.Â
